Maritz Travel, a Maritz Global Events company, works with meeting planners, sales operations and procurement teams to deliver business meetings and incentive travel programs for corporate, Fortune 100 companies. We help our clients create exceptional experiences through innovative design, flawless execution, leading-edge technology solutions, and our extensive partner network throughout North America and across the globe.
Solutions provided by Maritz Travel:

Meetings and incentive travel design
Sourcing, site selection and contract negotiation
Web registration, ticketing and attendee services
Creative communications
Registration, mobile and social technology
On-site support
Reporting and analytics

 
 
INCENTIVES AND REWARDS | MEETINGS AND EVENTS
view website




























Experient, a Maritz Global Events company, works with meeting planners, executive administrators and marketing professionals in the government, association and tradeshow markets, providing meeting and event services. Our team helps clients deliver end-to-end event experiences from registration and housing services to event management solutions throughout North America and across the globe.
Solutions provided by Experient:

Advanced and on-site registration
Lead retrieval
Room block management
Mobile event apps
Meeting planning
Sourcing and contract negotiation
On-site support

 
 
