                            Our Companies
                        






























Maritz Motivation Solutions works with marketing, human resources, and sales and channel marketing executives to provide consumer loyalty, channel loyalty, employee engagement and sales incentive solutions to Fortune 100 companies. Our teams help clients achieve business results by designing and delivering programs that engage and motivate people, are simple to use and manage, and make people feel special.
Solutions provided by Maritz Motivation Solutions:

Employee Engagement and Recognition 
Customer Loyalty
Sales Incentives 
Channel Loyalty 
Rewards 

 
 
CUSTOMER LOYALTY PROGRAMS | EMPLOYEE ENGAGEMENT & RECOGNITION | INCENTIVES AND REWARDS
view website




























MaritzCX works with customer experience management professionals and market researchers to provide a customer experience software and research solution that helps organizations understand and respond to customer experiences in real time. With our scalable software platform and research expertise we help clients deliver exceptional customer experiences and greater revenue, growth and retention.
Solutions provided by MaritzCX:

CX strategy, design and program management
Data collection and spotlight data mining
Analytics, dashboards and reporting
Surveys, text analytics and case management
Consultative services
Mystery shopping

 
 
CUSTOMER EXPERIENCE TECHNOLOGY
view website




























Maritz Global Events partners with meeting and event industry professionals to help prove the value of face-to-face meetings. Maritz Global Events and its family of brands – Maritz Travel and Experient – design and deliver face-to-face meetings and global experiences for clients and their guests, everywhere in the world.  Through our deep expertise, unparalleled buying power, unique experience design methodology and distinctive approach to global meetings, we provide our customers with events that create real business results. 
Focus Areas and Priorities provided by Maritz Global Events:

Global meetings capabilities, a comprehensive network of partners with deep cultural ties throughout the world 
Experience design methodology, a people-centered, science-based approach to event design 
Business value of events approach, extensive thought leadership that showcases the power face-to-face meetings have in moving business forward and achieving results
The fight to end human trafficking initiative, a commitment to provide awareness, tools and support to the tourism industry 

 
 

