Johannes S. Maritz 
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President, Human Resources at JOY GLOBAL INC, Johannes S. Maritz  made $1,182,311 in total compensation.  Of this total $387,338 was received as a salary, $0 was received as a bonus, $186,760 was received in stock options, $489,582 was awarded as stock and $118,631 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2015 fiscal year. 


